DINNER AND OR MOVIE NIGHT
Jesse's RESTAURANT
ROUTE 120
HANOVER, NH 03755
603-643-4111

DINNER AND CONVERSATION AT 5:00- 5:15

Come join JanetM 56 for an evening of conversation and dinner with group discussion of the choice of movie. The event has been successful, so come and join those of us who have made a great evening out in the Upper Valley. Not obligated for the dinner but come and join us for the movie, or just come for the dinner, your choice. With two choices for movies, dinner is early to be able catch either movie theater, The Nugget, or the Cinema 6 in Lebanon, NH.
Look forward in meeting you, and spending a great evening with movie and dinner.

JanetM56; redscarlet56@gmail.com; 802-282-6202
item.how_to_find_us: Ask the Hostesses for Janet's table/ or look for the Meetup flyers
